name: Vintage Sparrow Bracelet
description:
This Sparrow Vintaj Bracelet is stylish, fun, and very Vintaj. 

All the beads you see are included; freshwater pearl, natural agate gemstone, sparrow Vintaj pendant, Vintaj teensie lizard, Vintaj chain and findings. The bracelet is made of brass and is also lead free. 

All Vintaj jewelry will be polished before it leaves my store. 

This bracelet measures 7.50 inches in length. If you need it longer I can add another loop. Let me know when ordering. 

All jewelry purchased from my store will be placed in a pink organza gift bag and wrapped in tissue paper ready to give to that special someone
